freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: For a couple of days about 2 wks after the shot I had some aching in my left shoulder where I had the shot. But it is better now.
Shortness of breath. It comes and goes.
Upper respiratory infection. Shortness of breath, Coughing & some wheezing.
